# Project Configuration

## Project Type
- Marketing website with modern design and simple contact functionality

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14+ with App Router
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Optional: Minimal Supabase usage for contact form submissions
- Vercel for deployment
- GitHub for version control

## Project Structure
/src
  /app         # Next.js App Router pages
  /components  # React components
  /lib         # Utility functions
  /types       # TypeScript types
/public        # Static assets

## Content Focus
- Clear presentation of marketing information
- Strategic placement of call-to-action elements
- Responsive design for all device sizes
- Performance optimization for fast page loads

## Development Workflow
- Cline helps write and review code changes
- Vercel automatically deploys from main branch
- Focus on design consistency and user experience

## SEO Considerations
- Semantic HTML structure
- Proper metadata for pages
- Optimized image sizes and loading
- Core Web Vitals optimization

## Security
DO NOT read or modify:
- .env files
- **/config/secrets.*
- Any file containing API keys or credentials
